snippet.textDisplay:
My heart sank when it transformed into is cloud form. It was going to circle around me and then charge at me mid air, killing me instantly. It was over i was going to die thinking that i could achieve anything i sought out.

Then i remembered.If i time it correctly i could use the Blue Slash technique to slay the mid air. But that was unlikely, i never used that technique in 50 year's.

But as it was getting closer I knew i had to try. I whisperd the incantation and prayed to the gods that i would live to smell fresh air, see the sky and Embrace my daughter once more. The time came, i closed my eyes and i slashed the monster with every bit of energy i had. After a minute i opened my eyes. To see the monster turn to dust
